{"word":"H3289 - יָעַץ - yâʻats - yaw-ats' - Advertise","slug":"H3289","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">יָעַץ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>yâʻats"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>yaw-ats'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Advertise"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D9;&#x05E2;&#x05E5; - ya&#x0302;&#x201B;ats</b> - <i>yaw-ats'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>advise</i>; reflexively to <i>deliberate</i> or <i>resolve: - </i>advertise, take advice, advise (well), consult, (give take) counsel (-lor), determine, devise, guide, purpose."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4156\">H4156</a>, <a href=\"#/H6098\">H6098</a>"}]}